{"tid":1388782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好畀錢施捨冇錢開飯嘅抗爭巴打","createTime":"2019-07-30T18:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T19:22:59.000Z","uid":233118,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4c9db0316eb2cfab14be41bfe12f6ec58217c79e","tid":1388782,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:36:49.000Z","msg":"人係有尊嚴，有骨氣<br />\n<br />\n佢哋肯即使捱餓都要買裝備抗爭<br />\n<br />\n證明佢哋係真心愛香港，肯為咗香港而犧牲<br />\n<br />\n你咁樣無條件咁畀食物同裝備佢，喺施捨，係可憐佢，咁令到佢地更加心噏<br />\n<br />\n嘢食係要買，裝備係要畀<br />\n<br />\n但唔係無條件咁畀，喺<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">借</span></span><br />\n<br />\n用乜嘢嚟還？<br />\n<br />\n同佢哋講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">用抗爭勝利同香港嘅未來嚟還</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔該大家<br />\n<br />\n唔好令到前線難堪<br />\n<br />\n多謝"},{"pid":"479815db1934b4dbf3ec31064b06583dc9f5297a","tid":1388782,"uid":233118,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:38:21.000Z","msg":"人係唔會無端白事接受無條件嘅施捨<br />\n<br />\n用借嘅話反而合理化成件事<br />\n<br />\n大家既可以互相打氣<br />\n<br />\n亦都可以避免雙方面子受損"},{"pid":"573e9721d2dcbce0c555d8eb7bdf00cd457b36e5","tid":1388782,"uid":233118,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:39:40.000Z","msg":"唔好再用一種可憐嘅語氣去散佈義士冇錢開飯， 我係個義士都會覺得難堪"},{"pid":"37243e0a270770068201be927a3cb07474530a61","tid":1388782,"uid":44751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ygGROuK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FygGROuK.png&h=dac11253&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01d5848da003fa264ffcbe55742c6c60d472cfc7","tid":1388782,"uid":233118,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:40:44.000Z","msg":"佢哋為咗香港付出咁多<br />\n<br />\n唔該畀返尊嚴佢哋<br />\n<br />\n唔好當人哋乞衣<br />\n<br />\n你而家係要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">借</span>裝備畀佢哋"},{"pid":"60d40358bb4d48b368a385bf869328fb69ed404f","tid":1388782,"uid":233118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:42:02.000Z","msg":"試著說為香港奉獻一切<br />\n<br />\n不要說為抗爭窮到冇錢開飯"},{"pid":"7659bfa108f96a1f9865592b67339dbb01b798ed","tid":1388782,"uid":67223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:43:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"955e6a7e2dfb4ad46274631cadfbc9cb4e246ea0","tid":1388782,"uid":233118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:43:34.000Z","msg":"試著說 我借一頓飯給你，你現在要做的就是去打勝仗<br />\n<br />\n不要說 快吃吧 不要餓著了"},{"pid":"81af9fe29c5eb39db735c5bfa0e28541fbe1d403","tid":1388782,"uid":240732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:44:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://觀塘Galaxy.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98Galaxy.hk&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=7407d914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">觀塘Galaxy.hk</a>老闆係舖頭放置咗KFC禮卷 大家有需要可以上去拎 <br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！"},{"pid":"b4b1c7326b5cfd98d3a3c043628f1cb9329c8282","tid":1388782,"uid":233118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:45:36.000Z","msg":"我而家畀裝備你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你要做嘅就係抗爭到底，攞返香港嘅未來<br />\n<br />\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n唔好整傷自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢件裝備我畀你啦"},{"pid":"37be6337cdba683f9e62d48a473400acc191d80d","tid":1388782,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81af9fe29c5eb39db735c5bfa0e28541fbe1d403","tid":1388782,"uid":240732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:44:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://觀塘Galaxy.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98Galaxy.hk&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=7407d914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">觀塘Galaxy.hk</a>老闆係舖頭放置咗KFC禮卷 大家有需要可以上去拎 <br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:46:18.0